You must maintain at least one valid payment method in your ikigaiAir Account at any time. You’ll get Notified by Email a few days before the next monthly payment. Any medium or large modifications to the current services activated may result in charges being applied to your saved payment method, and charges may include taxes as required by law. Your failure to maintain accurate, complete, and up-to-date payment information, including an invalid or expired payment method, may result in your inability to access or use ikigaiAir.


